pageProduct.name: Thompson's Natural Super Carotene 60 Capsules
pageProduct.description:
General Information

Thompson's Natural Super Carotene helps maintain healthy eyes,
eyesight and night vision.

Thompson's Natural Super Carotene helps maintain healthy eyes, eyesight and night vision. It also helps support healthy immune system function, protect the skin against the harmful effects of UV light and relieve minor sunburn symptoms. Super Carotene is a natural, plant based multi-carotene supplement, rich in Beta-Carotene and other important antioxidants which help protect cells from free radical damage and maintain general wellbeing.

Size: 60caps

Oil-Free?: Yes

KEY FEATURES

• Helps maintain healthy eyes, eyesight and night vision.
• Helps support healthy immune system function.
• Helps protect the skin against the harmful effects of UV light and relieve minor sunburn symptoms.
• Help protect cells from free radical damage and maintain general wellbeing.

Warnings

If symptoms persist consult your healthcare professional. Vitamin supplements should not replace a balanced diet.

Ingredients

Active Ingredients: Each capsule contains: Herbal extract equiv. to fresh:
Dunaliella salina (Dunaliella) whole plant 312mg
equiv. Betacarotene 12.5mg

Allergen Free From: Added Sugar

Directions

Store below 30°C in a dry place. Do not use if bottle and/or cap seal is missing or broken. Keep out of reach of children.

Storage Temperature: Below 30°C

Recyclable Packaging?: Yes
